    <item>
      <title>Gentle Stretch</title>
      <link>https://yamadamay.dev/posts/gentle-stretch/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 20:32:40 +0900</pubDate>
      <guid>https://yamadamay.dev/posts/gentle-stretch/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I step into the bathroom.&#xA;I leave the light turn off.&#xA;Sunlight drifts in.&#xA;I sink into the bathtub.&#xA;Warm blood stirs.&#xA;I let out a breath.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
